<PB REF="027594_0002_0FD54D2590192B88" MS="y">
<P>THE TRIAL OF MAURICE MARGAROT, BEFORE THE HIGH COURT OF JUSTICIARY, <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 span"> On the <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 span"> 14th <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 span">, 1794, <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 word"> INDICTMENT FOR SEDITIOUS PRACTICES.</P>
<P><HI>TAKEN IN SHORTHAND</HI> BY MR. RAMSEY.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON: PRINTED.&mdash;NEW-YORK: RE-PRINTED,</HI> BY JAMES CAREY, No. 91, BROAD-STREET.</P>
</DIV1>
