<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lord Ju&s;tice Clerk.</SPEAKER>
<P> Surely both Pro&s;ecutor and Pannel ought to &s;ee that their witne&s;&s;es are all here. Let the Macer go now and &s;ee that they are here.</P>
