<P> And likewi&s;e that the Court and the people at large may be informed the rea&s;on why I have not the privilege of having you as an exculpatory evidence, in con&s;equence of the fear of the Me&s;&s;enger to deliver &s;uch a &s;ummons to you; that is a thing proper to be known.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="25" REF="027594_0025_0FD9B87E66160000">
<SPEAKER>Lord Ju&s;tice Clerk.</SPEAKER>
<P>If you have any thing that it is nece&s;&s;ary for me to prove, you &s;hall have the benefit of my te&s;timony, and you &s;hall not want it neither.</P>
